      <title>缅甸军政府势将失去动荡的政权，落入少数民族武装团体之手</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/myanmar-junta-set-to-lose-restive-state-to-ethnic-armed-group</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一份新报告显示，缅甸军政府即将被驱逐出缅甸最西部与孟加拉国接壤的一个邦，这是自 2021 年政变导致全国再次爆发民间冲突以来，缅甸军政府遭受的最大损失之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/myanmar-junta-set-to-lose-restive-state-to-ethnic-armed-group</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
